  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">NCCP 2017 Project DRR Advocacy</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1. Amplify the voice of NCCP on DRR and other related issues
2. Create a platform for FBOs to strengthen coordination and pursue collaboration on DRR and humanitarian response
3. Promote the unique perspective and values of FBOs pursuing common agenda on DRR.
4. Design and implement a strong advocacy program on DRR by building on the resources of FBOs, including NCCP member churches through the regional ecumenical councils.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthen and enhanced the capacity of faith-based organizations in disaster risk reduction and humanitarian advocacy.

1. A platform of FBOs doing DRR and humanitarian work in the Philippines is formed
2. Representation of NCCP RECs explore participation in the local disaster risk reduction and management councils
3. A clear mechanism on coordination and possible collaboration among FBOs.
4. An effective communications plan on DRR and humanitarian advocacy.</narrative>
  </description>
